in August of 2005,
the hurricane destroyed some of

00:40:05.126 --> 00:40:12.010
our refining capability and some
of our storage tanks because New

00:40:12.010 --> 00:40:18.571
Orleans is an oil center where
tankers come and they go up the

00:40:18.571 --> 00:40:22.924
